OL,4,Ctourism with 'barriers to travel'
OL,6,FThe Government has been accused of
OL,7,F"sabotaging" the UK's tourism industry
OL,8,Fas analysis found spending by
OL,9,Finternational visitors was more than
OL,10,F#2.2 billion below pre-pandemic levels
OL,11,Flast year.
OL,13,FA report by the London-based World
OL,14,FTravel and Tourism Council (WTTC),
OL,15,Fwhich represents the sector, found
OL,16,Fpeople visiting the UK spent #40.3
OL,17,Fbillion in 2024, down 5.3% from 2019.
