OL,6,FJulia Simpson, who is president of the
OL,7,FWTTC and was an adviser to Sir Tony
OL,8,FBlair during his time as prime
OL,9,Fminister, attributed the decline to
OL,10,Fmeasures she described as "deliberate
OL,11,Fpolicy choices" which have created
OL,12,F"barriers to travel".
OL,14,FThese include introducing electronic
OL,15,Ftravel authorisations ` digital
OL,16,Fpermits ` the lack of tax-free
OL,17,Fshopping and increasing air passenger
OL,18,Fduty.
