OL,6,FMs Simpson told the PA news agency:
OL,7,F"We've not got back to where we need
OL,8,Fto be (on spending by international
OL,9,Fvisitors), whereas the rest of the
OL,10,Fworld has.
OL,12,F"The UK is losing value share compared
OL,13,Fto other European partners.
OL,15,F"This Government is all about growth.
OL,16,FThey're looking at how to make money.
OL,17,FThey're trying to save steel plants.
OL,18,FThey're looking to see what can we do
OL,19,Fabout our water companies.
