OL,6,F"Yet here we have a private sector
OL,7,Fenterprise ` travel and tourism `
OL,8,Fcontributing 10% of UK GDP, creating
OL,9,Fjobs, but we are not prioritising it
OL,10,Fin any way.
OL,12,F"We are sabotaging ourselves."
OL,14,FThe report, produced in collaboration
OL,15,Fwith consultancy Oxford Economics,
OL,16,Falso found that travel and tourism
OL,17,Fcontributed #286 billion to the UK's
OL,18,Feconomy in 2024, up 3.9% from 2019.
