OL,11,Fcut tourism authority VisitBritain's
OL,12,Fbudget by "more than 40%".
OL,14,FShe said the Government is "very keen
OL,15,Fto promote the regions" but "to do
OL,16,Fthat you need a marketing wing".
OL,18,FShe continued: "You need to sell the
OL,19,FUK. You need to sell Harry Potter. You
OL,20,Fneed to sell Jane Austen. You need to
OL,21,Fsell Richard III.
